Last updated on June 26, 2024
1. Introduction
Libro.fm is committed to respecting the privacy rights and concerns of all users of our Service. The Libro.fm Service includes (a) any internet sites operated by Libro.fm, including without limitation the Libro.fm website at
https://libro.fm/
